            <abstract>
                <p>Two miniatures illustrating <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3586Miracle"/> in several episodes. The first miniature depicts in the first episode  <persName ref="PRS5555Ildefons"/> handing over to <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/>
                    the finished book of the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2384Taamme"/>, which she blesses and returns to him. In the second episode, <persName ref="PRS6819Mary"/> presents
                    to <persName ref="PRS5555Ildefons"/> a throne and garment. In the first episode of the second miniature, <persName ref="PRS5555Ildefons"/>
                    is represented sitting on the throne and reading from the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2384Taamme"/>. The second episode shows the stripped throne and garment after the fall 
                    of <persName ref="PRS5555Ildefons"/>'s successor. In the last episode, <persName ref="PRS5555Ildefons"/>'s successor is depicted fallen and being smitten by
                    the <term key="angel">angel</term>. All episodes are accompanied by legends and captions.</p>
            </abstract>
